	<h2 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-174692124" class="story-title"> <a   href="//it.slashdot.org/story/24/08/07/1352252/disneys-password-sharing-crackdown-starts-in-earnest-next-month">Disney's Password-Sharing Crackdown Starts 'in Earnest' Next Month</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/7/24215224/disney-password-sharing-crackdown-september"  title="External link - https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/7/24215224/disney-password-sharing-crackdown-september" target="_blank"> (theverge.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
